data Precision         : indivisible | deci | centi | milli
                       | deciMilli | centiMilli | micro | deciMicro
                       | centiMicro | nano | deciNano | centiNano
                       | pico | deciPico | centiPico | femto
                       | deciFemto | centiFemto | atto


